Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've sealed off all the entrances around the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:11.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is still no sign of BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He took a boat and escaped by sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:20.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No one can escape from our system.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll notify you when he has landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Standby at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So he used the doll system.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we used to observe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:39.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even with that system he's so proud of, he still couldn't capture BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:53.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would give me a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:08.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My Suou is already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:09.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Filthy abomination... you're driving me crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:25.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Nobody is angry in an aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:33.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it! The mom I knew always used to smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:34.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:38.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe then, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarium? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:55.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...!
