Dialogue: 4,0:02:38.64,0:02:42.34,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I pursued my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:47.90,OPR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Demo sore mo tooi kioku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:47.90,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But that's also a distant memory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:51.85,OPR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kotae no nai mainichi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:51.85,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The each unanswered day-
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.49,0:02:55.66,OPR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Tada sugite iku jikan ga
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.49,0:02:55.66,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The time that is simply passing by-
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.39,0:03:00.32,OPR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kore kara saki dou naru no darou?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.39,0:03:00.32,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What will happen beyond now?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.93,OPR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Wakaranai...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.93,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}They don't know...
