Dialogue: 7,0:03:14.84,0:03:23.88,OPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No matter how broken today looks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:40.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Both Mom and Shion smiled at that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:45.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back to those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:05.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it a secret... between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Synchronization noise in the interior system detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The probability of surveillance has fallen drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are several tiny holes in the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd find him by blindly looking around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold if you sleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:23.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were accompanied by a male doll, but I didn't expect it to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:33.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't BK201 with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:39.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He becomes violent very easily, forces me to do some strange training,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and is a good for nothing drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:47.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But he stopped drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're a girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:54.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you thought I was Shion too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:06:00.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I might not even be Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:12.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you mixed it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:16.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The area around the aquarium has been off-limits for thirteen years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Am I mixing it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:40.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom taught me how to fold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everything as if it was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,About my mom and the aquarium...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:52.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's related to Mikhail Pavlichenko's life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But my father's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:00.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've got a lot of things to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:08.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My god... how did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So that's her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's younger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:23.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Her ankles are so slim. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those ankles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:35.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, you have some pretty nice ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:43.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your compliment, but I guess you didn't notice this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:51.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the contrast between your growing belly and slim ankles is mesmerizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:57.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Take my hand. It would be bad for the child if you were to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in Japan for business?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I used to study here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:14.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd suggest you quickly return to your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:21.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, you won't be able to see the sun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}And then... a few days later after I left Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Makimiya Asako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me for coming here without prior notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:51.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you some questions regarding Mr. Mikhail Pavlichenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the Syndicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The Syndicate? Did you just say the Syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to do with him or the Syndicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:17.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... that Professor Pavlichenko is a member of the Syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're working to stop the Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They have been lurking in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll definitely unveil them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:34.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please... tell me what happened between you and the Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:38.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And about Suou and Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've met her twice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The first time was in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And the other time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:54.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,when I joined the Syndicate, and went to a university in Moscow as a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The professor was researching something interesting at that university.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody knew a thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was hired as an agent for another faction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:22.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and infiltrated his lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:27.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That day, I took Shion and Suou to the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:31.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to give my husband his lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that? That's what it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those ankles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you did great, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:45.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I have to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou, are you coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When Papa's work is done, I want to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:10:59.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:06.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, the Syndicate's internal conflicts had reached a point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was framed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That day, at that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou died in that explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She died!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Episode 10    You Smile on that Fake Street Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Yin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:11.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Iza... na... mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:20.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No! Izanami... can't meet with Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A big disaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:33.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The old woman that holds the memories of the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The various different futures she recorded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Various?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The world is running...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:49.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A dreadful memory written in the Mitaka Documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And... and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:58.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect Hazuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know about Izanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Izanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:08.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami will kill the contractors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The 18th Research Lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:24.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:28.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or else... or else Hazuki-san will....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was done with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've done your job splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You brought her to Tokyo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But letting her go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:02.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A bullet was found in an incident at Oomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:06.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,as well as an anti-tank rifle, modified for a left-hander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Poor little red star...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Section 3 is going to treat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:20.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I searched for Suou after the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I ran... and ran... and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:29.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him using the ME on her lifeless body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mikhail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to our child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this exactly because she's our child!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:44.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be ours forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:54.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! My body is dog food now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Asako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:06.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You will regret this! Asako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:16.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion chose not to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:22.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I cremated Suou's body, and returned to Japan with her ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:29.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And today, Suou... no... her fake clone appeared in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She looked like Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:39.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Her downcast look and pale lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She was like a perfect clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Shion's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion Pavlichenko's... power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He defiled her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:59.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's a monster, created from his demented mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place for me to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:28.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't as shocked as I thought I'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because I'm a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or just a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:38.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think these things matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should cry if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:45.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guarantee your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No! She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in Section 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:19.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! But she gave me steamed buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Li-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Youko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Youko... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill BK201...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come back for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:20.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you were able to kill someone, you wouldn't need my help anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:24.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you be honest and apologize to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:31.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't shoot people, hence I can't become a real contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:35.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You used your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I copied it while I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little bit smaller though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Suou will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:52.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The fabricated memories we gave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:55.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A day with her family at the aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:59.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She’d be hurt even more if she found out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She has to learn what pain is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:06.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what color her pain would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:10.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The orange glow of a crescent moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can see the river from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:18.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The river in Sapporo was bigger and flowed faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:22.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is my memory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:29.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to call me like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to call out my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know of any other Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're a copy or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:52.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,you're the only Suou I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:03.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It hurt when you didn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It was much more painful than when you hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:14.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When you called my name, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I found out that it was to save Yin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And I was confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You killed my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good for nothing, violent drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:31.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, I feel so lonely without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mao! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about anything for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She cries a lot for a contractor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:04.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is she incomplete, because she's a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She can't control her feelings properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How much do we know about contractors?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:19.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's precisely because she's incomplete that she's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:24.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So, why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:27.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Does she resemble your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:33.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I saw myself in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:38.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're led by ignorance and incompleteness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:38.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:45.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,both of us don't have the time to be swayed around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:22:02.80,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:22:02.80,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:13.31,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:13.31,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:22.87,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:22.87,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:29.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:29.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.80,0:22:34.15,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.80,0:22:34.15,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.78,0:22:38.91,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.78,0:22:38.91,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:38.68,0:22:47.56,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:38.68,0:22:47.56,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:47.38,0:22:52.65,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:22:47.38,0:22:52.65,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.39,0:22:59.60,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.39,0:22:59.60,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:22:59.23,0:23:07.19,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:22:59.23,0:23:07.19,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:07.11,0:23:17.48,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:07.11,0:23:17.48,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:25.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:28.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:32.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:34.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:36.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:37.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty.
